snippet.title: Amber’s Airline – High Hopes: Story (Chapter 3) (Voice-Overs; Subtitles)
snippet.description:
What happened previously on “Amber’s Airline”: Pamela joined the flight crew; Amber was relegated to the security team. Elise’s dependency on pills increases. David and Amber had an enjoyable movie & popcorn date. Amber met Clark, an interesting doctor who travels a lot for work. Amber jumped at the opportunity to work in a Tahiti VIP lounge. A GameHouse Original Story (GHOS).

Play Now: https://go.onelink.me/GxDd
